				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A lower city denizen visits the Guildhall for a drink with his friend. In truth, he's being fed drink by this sober friend to keep him out of trouble. But he knows where to listen, and has learned the location of the Stone Lord's ambush. We can learn it from him if we put up with his shit long enough."
				}
